Re Datren Williams Acceptancea kind and thoughtful man you always are VinceI have always appreciated that in you I just moved to another position this week with Sheila Knudsen in ENA Compensation but I will always remember how wonderful you are with the Associates and Analysts in the Program and will miss having the opportunity to touch base with you occasionally Thank you for being the special man you are Carol PS I doubt that you know who I am but I had worked with the program for two years having been hired by Mike Smalling in October When I first moved to Houston from Ohio and Enron I rode the bus for a short while You helped me find Enron the first day I rode it but I didnt know who you were until I saw you at our Super Saturday activities You will never know how much that assistance meant to me a shy streetdumb girl from Toledo Ohio in a city like Houston who didnt know how to ride a bus All of Enron loves you and I know why Vince J Kaminski PM To Carol CT cc Subject Re Datren Williams Acceptance Carol Thanks Vince Carol Coats PM To Vince J CT cc Stinson CT Subject Re Datren Williams Acceptance You are right VinceCeleste and I did discuss it and she approved his Feb start date Datren does know about that so it sounds like it is cleared up Thanks so much and we are sorry for the confusion Carol Vince J Kaminski PM To Stinson CT cc Carol CT Subject Re Datren Williams Acceptance Stinson I think its a mistake It should be February Vince Stinson Gibner PM To Vince J CT cc Subject Datren Williams Acceptance FYI Forwarded by Stinson GibnerHOUECT on PM Carol Coats PM To Celeste CT cc Stinson CT Subject Datren Williams Acceptance Celeste I just received Datren Williams acceptance with the following note attached My graduation date PhD Candidate from LSU is Dec Celeste Roberts has informed me that I would have the option of starting work Feb I am under the impression that I will start in Feb My offer letter has a start date of Aug If this is a problem please give me a call Looking forward to working at Enron Thanks a million Datren W Please let me know if he may in fact start in Feb and if so do you have a specific date for him or may he choose Thanks Celeste Carol
